{"word":"G4891 - συνεγείρω - synegeírō - soon-eg-i'-ro - Raise up together","slug":"G4891","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνεγείρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>synegeírō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soon-eg-i'-ro"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Raise up together"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C9; - sunegeiro&#x0304;</b> - <i>soon-eg-i'-ro</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G1453\">G1453</a>; to <i>rouse</i> (from death) in company <i>with</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>revivify</i> (spiritually) in resemblance to: - raise up together, rise with."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888\">G4888</a>, <a href=\"#/G4916\">G4916</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957\">G4957</a>"}]}